"reviewcomment":"A couple weeks I was here looking for a bathing suit.  Michelle, the sales associate covering the department at the time was super helpful and patient.  I came across a swimsuit from the Juicy Couture Spring 2009 collection which was ticketed a regular price of $173.  Just an hour earlier, I was at the Juicy Couture store admiring the same suit, which was on sale there for $105, size XS.  When I mentioned how it was on sale elsewhere, Michelle right away mentioned that Nordstrom matches prices of other retailers.  Of course, when I heard that I nearly jumped for joy.  I asked Michelle to see if another store would have size small available.  She checked the system and to my luck, yes a size small was available.  As a gift, my mom ended up ordering the swimsuit which should get to me within a few days.  Next time I&#39;m in the swimsuit/athletic wear department at Nordstrom Union Square, I will definitely be back to purchase from Michelle.  She was so very pleasant to deal with.",
